    <p>We want there to be one million Dementia Friends by 2015 all using their understanding of dementia to create dementia friendly communities. Every action counts.</p><p>"We go and do the things together that we enjoy and we work on Sue's garden together." Wendy, friend of Sue who is living with dementia</p>    </div>                                <a href="/WEBArticle?page=what-is-a-friend" class="btn btn-primary">What is a Friend?</a>
